This project is a smart Arduino-based **Bluetooth-controlled Robocar** that can also **automatically avoid obstacles** using an HC-SR04 ultrasonic sensor.  
Control the robot manually using a mobile app (via HC-05), or put it on Automatic Mode for self-driving obstacle detection.

